node.text:
The Five Labours of Jericho has proven to be one of the greatest tests of all-time physically and psychologically for @chrisjerichofozzy. Can he overcome the odds one more time, even without all things Judas - the song and the Judas Effect?

Tune in as @the_mjf and Chris Jericho go head-to-head at last for the fifth & final Labour of Jericho TONIGHT on #AEWDynamite from Houston live on @tntdrama at 8/7c 🧨

node.title: Chris Jericho v MJF - AEW Dynamite

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by AEW on August 24, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'CHRIS JERICHO DISCUSSES HIS FUTURE LIVE LIVE! WEDNESDAY AUGUST 25 8/7c TNT @ALLELITEWRESTLING @AEW ALLELITEWRESTLING.CO CARD UBJECT O CHANGE'.

node.text:
As first announced tonight on #AEWDark, @chrisjerichofozzy will address his future TOMORROW on #AEWDynamite LIVE at 8/7c on TNT. After last week’s crushing loss to 
@The_MJF in the Final Labour of Jericho, #LeChampion has had time to do some soul-searching. What will he have to say?
